Beginning July 29, 2020 OUESD will resume the USDA National Breakfast and Lunch Programs.
Mondays and Thursdays* from 10 AM - 12 PM at ALL SITES
OR 4:30 - 6:30 pm at Delta Vista and Gehringer Schools.

On Wednesday, JULY 29th meals will be available from
10 am - 12 pm at ALL SITES, with the exception of Gehringer School, and from 4:30 - 6:30 pm at DELTA VISTA only.
(3 breakfast and 3 lunch meals will be provided for Wed., Thurs., & Fri.) *Meals will not be served on Thursday July 30th.

Meal Prices and additional information is available here:
English: rb.gy/9s0d0p | Español: https://rb.gy/qic95z

Mental Health and Social/Emotional Support Resources:
We want all of our Oakley Union Elementary School District community to know their health and safety is our priority. During times of uncertainty, it is important to concentrate on the physical and emotional health of students, staff, and families. We have created this COVID-19 resource page with various resources, activities and hotlines to reach out for assistance.

View the full list of resources: https://rb.gy/wges7o

In the event that this is an emergency, dial 9-1-1 for immediate help.
